    "materials_text": "Materials:\n1.        PCR 8-tube strips or 96 well plates depending on sample# and gene# (_General stores 4868_)\n1.        PCR strip tube lids\u00a0 (_General stores 1400-0800_)\n1.        ABI Sybr Green\u00a0 (_ABI 4301955_)\n1.        QPCR plate\u00a0 (_ABI 4309849_)\n1.        Adhesive plate film\u00a0 (ABI 4311971)\n1.        Brown plastic adhesive helper\n1.        Filtered 200 \u03bcl pipette tips (2 boxes for one complete plate)\n1.        Electronic Multichannel Pipette (referred to as Hilda from here on out)\n1.        Primers \u2013 final concentration of 1.25 \u03bcM each\n1.        Autoclaved MilliQ H2O",
